{"tid":1342710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大反攻】聽朝齊上電台/貼連儂牆控訴佢地︰(1) 全體建制派，不只何生 (2) 警察","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:33:12.000Z","uid":54684,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"183ba721c837e7291ef01f9d6eeec58e4af8e083","tid":1342710,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"今晚元朗咁大單野，係我地文宣既一個絕好機會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連儂牆︰Poster級，甚至Banner級既文宣係一定要做<br />\n街上︰Airdrop<br />\n電台︰一齊打上鬧爆！一定要</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1) 唔好只係blame何生，係全體建制派<br />\n何生同人握手既video流出左，佢衰硬，而建制派一定瘋狂割蓆<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，唔好只係控訴佢</span></strong><br />\n而係控訴佢全個建制派<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;白衫追打市民，事後<ins>建制派</ins>同白衫人士握手&quot;</span></strong>呢D title梗要</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;<ins>建制派</ins>疑組織白衫人追打市民，事後握手搭謝&quot;</span></strong>呢D title梗要</span><br />\n重要放埋youtube link, QR code<br />\n務求每個市民都睇到條握手片<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要blame，就blame全體建制派！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n(2) 警方<br />\n警方一定會拉少少白衫人擺出保護市民既姿態，文宣要做得快<br />\n<br />\n元朗地鐵度有差人走開左，然後白衣人出現打人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">專打黑衫</span></strong></span>，無警察到場<br />\n白衣人散左，警察先到場，重話全元朗得個十幾二十人，又叫市民唔好出街<br />\n12:30am左右，白衣人又返來打人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>依家咩世界？警黑合作！放手畀白衫打人！<br />\n相信唔少市民都會咁諗</strong></span></span><br />\n文宣一定要放埋呢個大指控<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣聽日就要做<br />\n愈遲，對家就一定有時間spin<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民情勝敗，就睇聽日，各位加油</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7f57840c8f0b5d355cc5901831a296a0e9613957","tid":1342710,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0e019d82fb9f1463aefe7f9980699b923aa87e","tid":1342710,"uid":133886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a339c9ee93cecc909902affcab19c9bcaf18bdc3","tid":1342710,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50056fb0f160d38e5903eb2cea4dcc2d0141c1b1","tid":1342710,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c32dfea954b115d6add6a53d75f24adcbc589e8","tid":1342710,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514be1350e5b60e69e3e293ef059fcb6c41df251","tid":1342710,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"屌冇人推"},{"pid":"05986c8ce9f4a5017a77e6bf75eab7d5e69f569f","tid":1342710,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"係咪最後無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994b708c8ca2ebd18dd72ab59d61dcc545da1e68","tid":1342710,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"我宣布「政警鄉黑」大合作，「黑警、黑鄉、黑社會」合稱「三黑」，必須追究「三黑」暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1339336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1339336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a15856f96b449343562efbcd5bab477352e9fed","tid":1342710,"uid":247180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"push"}]}